    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1910-08-06T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1910-08-06T00:00:00-05:00" n="296"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d296">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 774/775.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Netherlands Minister</gloss> to the
                            <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Netherlands Legation</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Bar Harbor, Me.</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1910-08-06">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 6, 1910</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Am instructed inform your excellency that Chinese Government having urgently
                    requested postponement, my Government will propose later date for convening
                    opium conference.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Loudon.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
